content.text: Destroy job for jenkins is up and running:
https://jenkins.staging-amber.com/job/Dev/job/ECS-PR-Destroy/
Create PR job in jenkins is blocked for now due to following reasons:
- Jenkins is deployed on ecs, which supports two modes of deployments Fargat and EC2.
- Fargate launch type is on containers, and due to aws limitations we cannot create docker images on it:
- EC2 launch type requires and autoscale group and an instance constantly running but new tasks deployed on it are also run as containers, hence we can-not use those also.
